Type Of CSS :
    
    1.Inline
    2.Internal
    3.External

color -           for changing text color
background -      for changing background color  (ex:<p style="color:red;background:green;")
font-family -     to change text font type  (ex: Tempu Sans ITC, vivaldi, Tw Cen MT, Wide Latin,......)(ex:style="font-family:Wide Latin")
font-size -       to increase or decrease font size  (ex: 30px, 15px, 40px,.....) (style="font-size:12px")
letter-spacing -  ""         "        "    "     (ex: s="l-s:4px,6px")
word-spacing -    "            "        "      "   (ex: s="w-s:6px,4px")
text-align -      text is center and right and left sifded is using this(ex:styly="text-align:center & right & left;")


